      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '-Overview

        You Can Tap On The Screen To Investigate And Pick
        Up Items.

        Picked Up Items Are Displayed At The Top Of The Screen,

        You
        Can Select By Tapping.


        - Item Use

        If You Tap A Suspicious
        Place With An Item Selected,

        May Be Used.


        - Show Items
        Larger

        Double-Tap An Item To Make It Larger.


        - Use Items
        For Items

        With The Item Displayed Large, Select Another Item,

        If
        You Tap The Item Displayed In Large Size, The Item Will Be Added To The Item.

        Can
        Be Used.


        You Can See Hints When You Don''t Understand.


        Let''s
        Investigate Various Places So That We Can Escape.'
